# 💳 Online Payment Transaction System (Java)

## 📌 Project Description
A console-based Online Payment Processing System developed using Core Java.
The system simulates secure transactions with proper validation and exception handling.

## 🚀 Features
- Create User Account
- Add Balance
- Make Payment
- Transaction Validation
- Insufficient Balance Handling
- Custom Exception Handling
- Transaction History

## 🛠 Concepts Used
- OOP (Classes & Objects)
- Encapsulation
- Exception Handling
- Custom Exceptions
- Input Validation
- Transaction Logic

## 🔐 Validations Included
- Invalid Payment Amount
- Insufficient Balance
- Negative Input Handling
- Account Not Found

## ▶ How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Compile Java files
3. Run Main class

